summary: Into the Spider-Verse was awesome and here's why:
body:
Into the Spider-Verse was awesome and here’s why:

**Spoilers below, like a lot of spoilers**

-Okay so, this movie? Great. Like, really great. I loved it so much. Miles Morales is my son and did not deserve any of what happened.

-His parents? Amazing. We needed more of his mom.

-MILES SPEAKING SPANISH!!!!

-Okay so we get introduced to this universe’s Peter Parker (he’s blonde??) and they literally kill him within five minutes of meeting him.

-This movie is rated PG right?

-I love the shot composition, the colors, the transition effects, just everything. It’s so creatively shot, I need more.

*This movie needs a severe seizure warning before it because this movie could easily cause one with it’s erratic movement and colors*

-King Pin was terrifying and I loved the backstory.

-OLIVIA OCTAVIOUS!! YES!!

-Sam Raimi universe Peter is a walking dumpster fire and we love him.

“So you’re calling me fat?”

-Let’s be fair Peter, you’ve seen better days.

-GWEN STACEY!!! SHE’S AMAZING!!

-Okay she’s probably the only one who’s actually got her shit together and I love her and Miles taking to each other. They’re adorable.

-Spider Noir not knowing what color is, I love that.

“Also I punch Nazis.”

-Noice.

-John Mulaney as Spider-Ham is amazing.

“This guy is such a pig.”

“I’m right here.”

-Cartoon logic~

-Penni Parker is adorable.

-She’s psychic? I did not know that. I’ve honestly never read any of her comics and now I want to.

-Aunt May is a God damn bad ass.

“I said, TAKE THIS OUTSIDE!”

-MILES UNCLE IS THE PROWLER?! -wait I already knew that- BUT THEN HE DIED?!

-This last fight scene was such a mind fuck, I love it.

If you read this (and haven’t seen the movie yet) DO IT!! THIS WAS AWESOME AND DESERVES OUR MONEY!

summary: PSA there is a clip from community in Spider-Man: Into the Spiderverse with Donald Glover in the Spider-Man pajamas
body:
PSA there is a clip from community in Spider-Man: Into the Spiderverse with Donald Glover in the Spider-Man pajamas

For those who don’t know, there was a movement to get Donald Glover aka Childish Gambino cast as Spider-Man before Andrew Garfield was announced. This petition led to the creation of Miles Morales.

If you wanna see the clip, look at the TV when Miles first gets to Uncle Aaron’s apartment.
